<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>You can find them in karana not to far from TOWER 2, walk into the tower step out from the door look to your right run to the farm house be carefull. there is about 2 to 3 bandits a nd farmers that u can kill. make sure your at level 9 and up to be in the safe side. if u see houses that are shops your not there,but your close just face the houses<BR>
look to your right and keep walking, u will see a brown barn.<BR>
good luck</font></td></tr></table>
