<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Pilara</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-07-31 15:45:43</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>The bandits they are talking about are the Nibright Sisters (Shayla, Jayla, Tayla and Kayla).  As you come out of Mistmore zone, take a right and follow the wall.  The first small camp you come to is the bandit camp.  They range from 10 to about 17 or so, and drop some bronze weapons.  Exp is really good with a grp of 2 no more than 3.  I tried to solo them at 17 and they kicked my butt because spawn ratio is very high.  Also, they each drop Dull Pearl Necklaces (Collect all 4, hehehe), turn these in to Brandon Nibright (the Drunkard) in Kelethin for exp and armor.  Good Luck!!!<BR>
<BR>
18 Cleric - Rodcet Nife</font></td></tr></table>
